/output/
/output-*/
/.dl/
/.ccache/
/.home/

# Ren'Py-generated artifacts in bundled game overlays. The .rpy sources and real
# assets (images, audio) are tracked; bytecode and runtime state are derived.
# NOTE: these are copied verbatim into the rootfs, so a fresh-clone image ships
# without bytecode and Ren'Py recompiles on first launch (fine while root is
# writable; precompile at build time before Phase 5's read-only root).
*.rpyc
*.rpymc
*.rpyb
**/the_question/game/saves/
**/the_question/game/cache/
**/the_question/log.txt
**/the_question/traceback.txt
**/the_question/errors.txt
